Query.SQL: SELECTX(IDS-DB01) <XTAB 7;"2";"LIST";"CRLF";"F";"N";""> DISTINCT GenProcID FROM [dbo].[JobQueue] WHERE Ready2EXE = 'FROZEN' ORDER BY GENPROCID JOIN_ON GenProcID SELECTX(IDS-DB01) DISTINCT JobChainName FROM [dbo].[JobQueue] WHERE Ready2EXE = 'FROZEN' ORDER BY JOBCHAINNAME JOIN_ON GenProcID;JobChainName SELECTX(IDS-DB01) XDateInserted, TaskName, ParamIN, <DBLOOKUP(IDS-DB01,n/a,,DELL) "<OBJECT_TABLE>" "'<OBJECT_TABLE_NAME>'[Table Name], <DEFAULT>[Object Name]" "" "" "BasisObjectKey=XObjectKey">, BasisObjectKey, ErrorMessages, ComponentClass, JobChainName FROM [dbo].[JobQueue] WHERE Ready2EXE = 'FROZEN' ORDER BY XDATEINSERTED DESC;

SELECTX(IDS-DB01) <XTAB 7;"2";"LIST";"CRLF";"F";"N";""> DISTINCT GenProcID FROM [dbo].[JobQueue] WHERE Ready2EXE = 'FROZEN' ORDER BY GENPROCID JOIN_ON GenProcID SELECTX(IDS-DB01) DISTINCT JobChainName FROM [dbo].[JobQueue] WHERE Ready2EXE = 'FROZEN' ORDER BY JOBCHAINNAME JOIN_ON GenProcID;JobChainName SELECTX(IDS-DB01) XDateInserted, TaskName, ParamIN, <DBLOOKUP(IDS-DB01) "<OBJECT_TABLE>" "'<OBJECT_TABLE_NAME>'[Table Name], <DEFAULT>[Object Name]" "" "" "BasisObjectKey=XObjectKey">, BasisObjectKey, ErrorMessages, ComponentClass, JobChainName FROM [dbo].[JobQueue] WHERE Ready2EXE = 'FROZEN' ORDER BY XDATEINSERTED DESC;

WITH rpt AS ( select 'Job' As Obj, Name As ObjName, GenCondition As ObjScript from Job where not GenCondition is Null UNION select 'DialogScript' As Obj, ScriptName As ObjName, ScriptCode As ObjScript from DialogScript where not ScriptCode is Null UNION select 'DialogColumn' As Obj, UID_DialogTable + ' / ' + ColumnName As ObjName, Template As ObjScript from DialogColumn where not Template is Null UNION select 'DialogColumn' As Obj, UID_DialogTable + ' / ' + ColumnName As ObjName, FormatScript As ObjScript from DialogColumn where not FormatScript is Null UNION select 'JobParameter' As Obj, Name As ObjName, ValueTemplateDefault As ObjScript from JobParameter where not ValueTemplateDefault is Null UNION select 'DialogTable' As Obj, TableName As ObjName, OnSavingScript As ObjScript from DialogTable where not OnSavingScript is Null UNION select 'DialogTable' As Obj, TableName As ObjName, OnSavedScript from DialogTable where not OnSavedScript is Null UNION select 'DialogMethod' As Obj, MethodName As ObjName, MethodScript As ObjScript from DialogMethod where not MethodScript is Null UNION select 'DialogObject' As Obj, UID_DialogTable + ' / ' + ObjectName As ObjName, SelectScript As ObjScript from DialogObject where not SelectScript is Null UNION select 'DialogTree' As Obj, TreeNode As ObjName, StateScript As ObjScript from DialogTree where not StateScript is Null UNION select 'JobChain' As Obj, Name As ObjName, GenCondition As ObjScript from JobChain where not GenCondition is Null UNION select 'DPRTemplate' As Obj, DisplayName As ObjName, ScriptCode As ObjScript from DPRTemplate where not ScriptCode is Null UNION select 'JobRunParameter' As Obj, Name As ObjName, ValueTemplate As ObjScript from JobRunParameter where not ValueTemplate is Null ) SELECT Obj as "Table", ObjName as "Object", ObjScript as "Script" FROM rpt ORDER BY 1, 2, 3;

WITH v AS ( select 25 as wdt, 50 as uidlen, 'pro.cjib.minjus.nl' as root_domain, 10 as max_level ), GrpMembers (tak, UID_GroupDomain, UID_Group, GroupName, GroupFullName, GroupLevel, UID_MemberDomain, UID_Member, MemberName, MemberFullName, MemberLevel) AS ( -- root nodes with no children --SELECT -- 'root' as tak, -- gR.UID_ADSDomain as UID_GroupDomain, -- gR.UID_ADSGroup as UID_Group, -- gR.DistinguishedName AS GroupName, -- case when LEN(gR.cn) > v.wdt then -- cast('/' + substring(gR.cn,1,v.wdt-2) + '..' as varchar(2048)) -- else cast('/' + gR.cn as varchar(2048)) end as GroupFullName, -- 0 as GroupLevel, -- cast(null as varchar(38)) as UID_MemberDomain, -- cast(null as varchar(38)) as UID_Member, -- cast(null as varchar(38)) AS MemberName, -- cast(null as varchar(38)) AS MemberFullName, -- -1 as MemberLevel -- FROM v, ADSGroup gR -- INNER JOIN ADSDomain dR -- ON gR.UID_ADSDomain = dR.UID_ADSDomain -- WHERE 1=1 -- -- is not the child of one or more groups -- AND (not exists (select * from ADSGroupInADSGroup gggR where gggR.UID_ADSGroupParent = gR.UID_ADSGroup)) -- -- not a parent of another group -- AND (not exists (select * from ADSGroupInADSGroup gggR where gggR.UID_ADSGroupChild = gR.UID_ADSGroup)) -- AND dR.ADSDomainName = v.root_domain -- UNION ALL -- root nodes with children SELECT 'root' as tak, g0.UID_ADSDomain as UID_GroupDomain, g0.UID_ADSGroup as UID_Group, g0.DistinguishedName AS GroupName, case when LEN(g0.cn) > v.wdt then cast('/' + substring(g0.cn,1,v.wdt-2) + '..' as varchar(2048)) else cast('/' + g0.cn as varchar(2048)) end as GroupFullName, 0 as GroupLevel, gg0.UID_ADSDomain as UID_MemberDomain, gg0.UID_ADSGroup as UID_Member, gg0.DistinguishedName AS MemberName, case when LEN(g0.cn) > v.wdt then case when LEN(gg0.cn) > v.wdt then cast('/' + substring(g0.cn,1,v.wdt-2) + '..' + '/' + substring(gg0.cn,1,v.wdt-2) + '..' as varchar(2048)) else cast('/' + substring(g0.cn,1,v.wdt-2) + '..' + '/' + gg0.cn as varchar(2048)) end else case when LEN(gg0.cn) > v.wdt then cast('/' + g0.cn + '/' + substring(gg0.cn,1,v.wdt-2) + '..' as varchar(2048)) else cast('/' + g0.cn + '/' + gg0.cn as varchar(2048)) end end as MemberFullName, 1 as MemberLevel FROM v, ADSGroup g0 INNER JOIN ADSDomain d0 ON g0.UID_ADSDomain = d0.UID_ADSDomain INNER JOIN ADSGroupInADSGroup ggg0 on ggg0.UID_ADSGroupChild = g0.UID_ADSGroup -- is the child of one or more groups INNER JOIN ADSGroup gg0 on ggg0.UID_ADSGroupParent = gg0.UID_ADSGroup WHERE 1=1 -- not a parent of another group AND (not exists (select * from ADSGroupInADSGroup ggg0 where ggg0.UID_ADSGroupParent = g0.UID_ADSGroup)) --AND d0.ADSDomainName = v.root_domain UNION ALL -- nodes with parent and children SELECT 'node' as tak, gm1.UID_MemberDomain as UID_GroupDomain, gm1.UID_Member as UID_Group, gm1.MemberName AS GroupName, gm1.MemberFullName as GroupFullName, gm1.MemberLevel as GroupLevel, gg1.UID_ADSDomain as UID_MemberDomain, gg1.UID_ADSGroup as UID_Member, gg1.DistinguishedName AS MemberName, case when LEN(gg1.cn) > v.wdt then cast(gm1.MemberFullName + '/' + substring(gg1.cn,1,v.wdt-2) + '..' as varchar(2048)) else cast(gm1.MemberFullName + '/' + gg1.cn as varchar(2048)) end as MemberFullName, (gm1.MemberLevel + 1) as MemberLevel FROM v, GrpMembers gm1 -- has a parent INNER JOIN ADSGroup g1 ON gm1.UID_Member = g1.UID_ADSGroup -- has children INNER JOIN ADSGroupInADSGroup ggg1 ON ggg1.UID_ADSGroupChild = g1.UID_ADSGroup INNER JOIN ADSGroup gg1 on ggg1.UID_ADSGroupParent = gg1.UID_ADSGroup WHERE 1=1 AND gm1.MemberLevel < v.max_level UNION ALL -- leaf nodes without children SELECT 'leaf' as tak, gm2.UID_MemberDomain as UID_GroupDomain, gm2.UID_Member as UID_Group, gm2.MemberName AS GroupName, gm2.MemberFullName as GroupFullName, gm2.MemberLevel as GroupLevel, cast(null as varchar(38)) as UID_MemberDomain, cast(null as varchar(38)) as UID_Member, cast(null as varchar(38)) AS MemberName, cast(null as varchar(38)) AS MemberFullName, -1 as MemberLevel FROM v, GrpMembers gm2 INNER JOIN ADSGroup g2 ON gm2.UID_Member = g2.UID_ADSGroup -- has a parent -- has no children WHERE 1=1 AND (not exists (select * from ADSGroupInADSGroup ggg2 where ggg2.UID_ADSGroupChild = g2.UID_ADSGroup)) ), grps AS ( SELECT DISTINCT d.ADSDomainName As DomainName, GroupLevel as lev, GroupFullName as FullName, UID_Group As UID_ADSGroup, GroupName as DistinguishedName, tak FROM GrpMembers INNER JOIN ADSDomain d ON GrpMembers.UID_GroupDomain = d.UID_ADSDomain ), gaccts AS ( SELECT grps.DomainName, grps.lev, grps.FullName, grps.DistinguishedName, case when (ag.UID_ADSAccount is null) then 0 else case when (a.UID_Person is null) then 0 else 1 end end as pers_acct FROM grps LEFT OUTER JOIN ADSAccountInADSGroup ag ON grps.UID_ADSGroup = ag.UID_ADSGroup LEFT OUTER JOIN ADSAccount a ON a.UID_ADSAccount = ag.UID_ADSAccount ), group_hierarchy AS ( SELECT FullName, lev, DomainName, DistinguishedName, sum(pers_acct) as NumPersAccts FROM gaccts GROUP BY DistinguishedName, DomainName, FullName, lev ) SELECT FullName as "TREE: Full-path", lev as "<LEVEL>", DomainName as "Domain", DistinguishedName as "Group Distinguised-Name", NumPersAccts as "# AD Accounts" FROM group_hierarchy ORDER BY FullName;

as FullName, UID_Group As UID_ADSGroup, GroupName as DistinguishedName, tak FROM GrpMembers INNER JOIN ADSDomain d ON GrpMembers.UID_GroupDomain = d.UID_ADSDomain ), gaccts AS ( SELECT with ja as ( select p.CCC_PersonId, a.CCC_PriorityOrder, a.CCC_ContextId from dbo.Person p inner join dbo.LDAPAccount a on p.UID_Person = a.UID_Person ), multija as ( select CCC_PersonId, CCC_PriorityOrder, count(*) as NumJa from ja group by CCC_PersonId, CCC_PriorityOrder having count(*) > 1 ), dmultija as ( select distinct m.CCC_PersonId, p.InternalName from multija m inner join Person p on m.CCC_PersonId = p.CCC_PersonId ) selectx(1IM_PROD) CCC_PersonId, InternalName from dmultija order by 2 JOIN_ON CCC_PersonId selectx(1IM_PROD) CCC_ContextId, CCC_PriorityOrder, CCC_DateStartEffective, CCC_DateEndEffective, CCC_Status FROM LDAPAccount;

with v as ( select 'ATO' as domain ), pools as ( select cn, UID_ADSGroup from ADSGroup g where UID_ADSGroup in (select UID_ADSGroupChild from ADSGroupInADSGroup where UID_ADSGroupParent in (select UID_ADSGroup from ADSGroup where cn = 'G_Virtual Desktop Users')) ), accts as ( select p.cn as grp, p.UID_ADSGroup as uid, a.cn as acct from v, pools p inner join ADSAccountInADSGroup ag on p.UID_ADSGroup = ag.UID_ADSGroup inner join ADSAccount a on a.UID_ADSAccount = ag.UID_ADSAccount where p.cn like 'G_Desktop Pool ' + v.domain + '%' and not p.cn like '%TEST' ), cnts as ( select grp, uid, count(*) as 'NumAccts' from accts group by grp, uid ) selectx(1IM_PROD) cn from pools JOIN_ON UID_ADSGroup selectx(1IM_PROD) CanonicalName from ADSGroup;

with v as ( select 'ATO' as domain ), pools as ( select cn, UID_ADSGroup from ADSGroup g where UID_ADSGroup in (select UID_ADSGroupChild from ADSGroupInADSGroup where UID_ADSGroupParent in (select UID_ADSGroup from ADSGroup where cn = 'G_Virtual Desktop Users')) ), accts as ( select p.cn as grp, p.UID_ADSGroup as uid, a.cn as acct from v, pools p inner join ADSAccountInADSGroup ag on p.UID_ADSGroup = ag.UID_ADSGroup inner join ADSAccount a on a.UID_ADSAccount = ag.UID_ADSAccount where p.cn like 'G_Desktop Pool ' + v.domain + '%' and not p.cn like '%TEST' ), cnts as ( select grp, uid, count(*) as 'NumAccts' from accts group by grp, uid ) selectx(1IM_PROD) cn from pools JOIN_ON UID_ADSGroup selectx(1IM_PROD) SAMAccountName, cn, DisplayName, Description, Info from ADSGroup;

Query.Description: Persons with multi 1 or 2 or 3 or 4 priorities and Persons with no Active Job-Assignments
Query.SQL:
with ja as ( select p.CCC_PersonId, a.CCC_PriorityOrder, a.CCC_Status, a.CCC_ContextId from dbo.Person p inner join dbo.LDAPAccount a on p.UID_Person = a.UID_Person ), --select * from ja jatab as ( select CCC_PersonId, case when CCC_PriorityOrder = 1 then 1 else 0 end as prio_1, case when CCC_PriorityOrder = 2 then 1 else 0 end as prio_2, case when CCC_PriorityOrder = 3 then 1 else 0 end as prio_3, case when CCC_PriorityOrder = 4 then 1 else 0 end as prio_4, case when CCC_Status = 'Inactive' then 1 else 0 end as inact, case when CCC_Status = 'Active' then 1 else 0 end as act, case when CCC_Status = 'ActivePending' then 1 else 0 end as act_pend from ja ), tot as ( select distinct p.CCC_PersonId, p.InternalName, sum(prio_1) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as prio_1, sum(prio_2) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as prio_2, sum(prio_3) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as prio_3, sum(prio_4) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as prio_4, sum(inact) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as inact, sum(act) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as act, sum(act_pend) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as act_pend from jatab j inner join Person p on j.CCC_PersonId = p.CCC_PersonId ) selectx(1IM_PROD) CCC_PersonId, InternalName from tot where (inact > 0 and act = 0 and act_pend = 0) or (prio_1 > 1 or prio_2 > 1 or prio_3 > 1 or prio_4 > 1) order by InternalName JOIN_ON CCC_PersonId selectx(1IM_PROD) CCC_ContextId, CCC_PriorityOrder, CCC_DateStartEffective, CCC_DateEndEffective, CCC_Status
FROM LDAPAccount ORDER BY CCC_DateStartEffective;

Query.SQL: with ja as ( select p.CCC_PersonId, a.CCC_PriorityOrder, a.CCC_Status, a.CCC_ContextId from dbo.Person p inner join dbo.LDAPAccount a on p.UID_Person = a.UID_Person ), --select * from ja jatab as ( select CCC_PersonId, case when CCC_PriorityOrder = 1 then 1 else 0 end as prio_1, case when CCC_PriorityOrder = 2 then 1 else 0 end as prio_2, case when CCC_PriorityOrder = 3 then 1 else 0 end as prio_3, case when CCC_PriorityOrder = 4 then 1 else 0 end as prio_4, case when CCC_Status = 'Inactive' then 1 else 0 end as inact, case when CCC_Status = 'Active' then 1 else 0 end as act, case when CCC_Status = 'ActivePending' then 1 else 0 end as act_pend from ja ), tot as ( select distinct p.CCC_PersonId, p.InternalName, p.ExitDate, p.IsInActive, sum(prio_1) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as prio_1, sum(prio_2) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as prio_2, sum(prio_3) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as prio_3, sum(prio_4) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as prio_4, sum(inact) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as inact, sum(act) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as act, sum(act_pend) over(partition by j.CCC_PersonId) as act_pend from jatab j inner join Person p on j.CCC_PersonId = p.CCC_PersonId ) selectx(1IM_PROD) CCC_PersonId, InternalName, ExitDate, IsInActive from tot where (inact > 0 and act = 0 and act_pend = 0) or (prio_1 > 1 or prio_2 > 1 or prio_3 > 1 or prio_4 > 1) order by InternalName JOIN_ON CCC_PersonId selectx(1IM_PROD) CCC_ContextId, CCC_PriorityOrder, CCC_DateStartEffective, CCC_DateEndEffective, CCC_Status FROM LDAPAccount ORDER BY CCC_DateStartEffective;

WITH v AS ( select 25 as wdt, 50 as uidlen, 10 as max_level ), Members As ( SELECT 1 as lev, rN.UID_ITShopOrg as UID_Org, rN.Ident_Org as Org, rN.ITShopInfo as OrgInfo, cast('/' + substring(rN.Ident_Org,1,v.wdt) as varchar(2048)) as FullName FROM v, ITShopOrg rN WHERE rN.UID_ParentITShopOrg is null UNION ALL SELECT (r1.lev + 1) as lev, rr1.UID_ITShopOrg as UID_Org, rr1.Ident_Org as Org, rr1.ITShopInfo as OrgInfo, cast(r1.FullName + '/' + substring(rr1.Ident_Org,1,v.wdt) as varchar(2048)) as FullName FROM v, Members r1 INNER JOIN ITShopOrg rr1 ON rr1.UID_ParentITShopOrg = r1.UID_Org ), WITH items AS ( SELECT m.OrgInfo as OrgInfo, m.FullName as FullName, m.lev as lev, m.Org Org, ac.Ident_AccProduct as Prod, ac.UID_AccProduct as UID_Prod FROM Members m LEFT OUTER JOIN AccProduct ac ON ac.UID_AccProduct = m.UID_AccProduct ) SELECTX(IDS_D1IM_8) OrgInfo as "Object Type", FullName as "TREE: Full-path", lev as "<LEVEL>", Org as "Object Name", Prod as "Service Item" FROM items ORDER BY FullName JOIN_ON UID_Prod=UID_AccProduct WITH ents AS ( SELECT XObjectKey, 'ADSGroup' As TabName, 'Active Directory groups' As TabDescr FROM ADSGroup WHERE Query.Description: P-Direct Org Eenheden vs PIMS Afdelingen
Query.SQL: WITH v AS ( select 25 as wdt, 50 as uidlen, 10 as max_level ), dept AS ( SELECT ac.ObjectID, ac.DepartmentName, ac.ShortName, ac.Remarks, ac.treelevel, ac.FullPath, ac.UID_Department, ac.UID_ParentDepartment FROM Department ac INNER JOIN OrgType t ON ac.UID_OrgType = t.UID_OrgType WHERE (t.Ident_OrgType = 'P-Direct OrganizatieEenheid' And not ac.ObjectID is null) or (ac.ObjectID = '99990000') ), Members As ( SELECT cast('no parent' as varchar(20)) as typ, 1 as lev, rN.UID_Department, rN.ObjectID, cast('/' + substring(rN.DepartmentName,1,v.wdt) as varchar(2048)) as FullName FROM v, dept rN WHERE rN.Remarks is null UNION ALL SELECT cast('missing parent' as varchar(20)) as typ, 1 as lev, rN.UID_Department, rN.ObjectID, cast('/' + substring(rN.DepartmentName,1,v.wdt) as varchar(2048)) as FullName FROM v, dept rN WHERE not (rN.Remarks is null) and not (exists (select * from dept dt where dt.ObjectID = rN.Remarks)) UNION ALL SELECT cast('with parent' as varchar(20)) as typ, (r1.lev + 1) as lev, rr1.UID_Department, rr1.ObjectID, cast(r1.FullName + '/' + substring(rr1.DepartmentName,1,v.wdt) as varchar(2048)) as FullName FROM v, Members r1 INNER JOIN dept rr1 ON rr1.Remarks = r1.ObjectID WHERE r1.lev < v.max_level ), items AS ( SELECT m.typ, m.FullName as FullName, m.lev as lev, ac.ObjectID, ac.DepartmentName, ac.ShortName, ac.Remarks, ac.treelevel, ac.FullPath, ac.UID_Department FROM Members m INNER JOIN Department ac ON ac.UID_Department = m.UID_Department ) SELECTX(IDS-D1iM_8) FullName as "TREE: Full-path", lev as "<LEVEL>", ObjectID as "Organisatie Eenheid Nummer", ShortName as "Organisatie Eenheid ID", DepartmentName as "Organisatie Eenheid" FROM items ORDER BY FullName JOIN_ON UID_Department=CCC_UID_New_Department SELECTX(IDS-D1iM_8) <NONE> FROM CCC_Department_Map JOIN_ON CCC_UID_Old_Department=UID_Department SELECTX(IDS-D1iM_8) DepartmentName as "PIMS Department", ObjectID as "PIMS AfdelingID" FROM Department;

SELECTX(IDS-D1IM_8,svcIDS_sql,,V7) PDirFullPath, PDirTreeLevel, PDirOrgEenheidsNummer, PDirOrgEenheidsAfk, PDirDepartmentName, PimsDepartmentName, PimsAfdelingID, PimsDirectieCode, PimsDirectieName, PimsDienstCode, PimsDienstName, PimsAfdelingCode, PimsAfdelingName, PimsSubAfdelingCode, PimsSubAfdelingName FROM dbo.CCC_PDir_PIMS_Departments ORDER BY PDirFullPath;

WITH pdir AS ( SELECT * FROM Department WHERE UID_OrgType in (select UID_OrgType from OrgType where Ident_OrgType = 'P-Direct OrganizatieEenheid') ), pims AS ( SELECT * FROM Department WHERE UID_OrgType in (select UID_OrgType from OrgType where Ident_OrgType = 'PIMS Afdeling') ), map AS ( SELECT pdir.FullPath as PDirFullPath, pdir.treelevel as PDirTreeLevel, pdir.ObjectID as PDirOrgEenheidsNummer, pdir.ShortName as PDirOrgEenheidsAfk, pdir.DepartmentName as PDirDepartmentName, REPLACE(pims.FullPath,'PIMS Departments(99990001)','') as PimsFullPath, pims.treelevel as PimsTreeLevel, pims.DepartmentName as PimsDepartmentName, pims.ObjectID As PimsAfdelingID, CASE WHEN LEN(pims.ObjectID) >= 4 THEN SUBSTRING(pims.ObjectID,1,4) ELSE '' END AS PimsDirectieCode, CASE WHEN LEN(pims.ObjectID) >= 9 THEN SUBSTRING(pims.ObjectID,6,4) ELSE '' END AS PimsDienstCode, CASE WHEN LEN(pims.ObjectID) >= 14 THEN SUBSTRING(pims.ObjectID,11,4) ELSE '' END AS PimsAfdelingCode, CASE WHEN LEN(pims.ObjectID) >= 19 THEN SUBSTRING(pims.ObjectID,16,4) ELSE '' END AS PimsSubAfdelingCode, pdir.UID_Department as UID_Pims_Department, pdir.UID_ParentDepartment as UID_Pims_ParentDepartment, pims.UID_Department as UID_PDir_Department, pims.UID_ParentDepartment as UID_PDir_ParentDepartment FROM pdir LEFT OUTER JOIN CCC_Department_Map map ON pdir.UID_Department = map.CCC_UID_New_Department LEFT OUTER JOIN pims ON pims.UID_Department = map.CCC_UID_Old_Department ), dirs AS ( SELECT map.PDirFullPath, map.PDirTreeLevel, map.PDirOrgEenheidsNummer, map.PDirOrgEenheidsAfk, map.PDirDepartmentName, map.PimsFullPath, map.PimsTreeLevel, map.PimsAfdelingID, map.PimsDepartmentName, map.PimsDirectieCode, directie.DepartmentName as PimsDirectieName, map.PimsDienstCode, dienst.DepartmentName as PimsDienstName, map.PimsAfdelingCode, afd.DepartmentName as PimsAfdelingName, map.PimsSubAfdelingCode, subafd.DepartmentName as PimsSubAfdelingName, UID_Pims_Department, UID_Pims_ParentDepartment, UID_PDir_Department, UID_PDir_ParentDepartment FROM map LEFT OUTER JOIN pims AS directie ON map.PimsDirectieCode = directie.ObjectID LEFT OUTER JOIN pims AS dienst ON map.PimsDirectieCode + '.' + map.PimsDienstCode = dienst.ObjectID LEFT OUTER JOIN pims AS afd ON map.PimsDirectieCode + '.' + map.PimsDienstCode + '.' + map.PimsAfdelingCode = afd.ObjectID LEFT OUTER JOIN pims AS subafd ON map.PimsDirectieCode + '.' + map.PimsDienstCode + '.' + map.PimsAfdelingCode + '.' + map.PimsSubAfdelingCode = subafd.ObjectID ) SELECTX(IDS-D1IM_8) PDirFullPath, PDirTreeLevel, PDirOrgEenheidsNummer, PDirOrgEenheidsAfk, PDirDepartmentName, PimsFullPath, PimsTreeLevel, PimsAfdelingID, PimsDepartmentName, PimsDirectieCode, PimsDirectieName, PimsDienstCode, PimsDienstName, PimsAfdelingCode, PimsAfdelingName, PimsSubAfdelingCode, PimsSubAfdelingName, UID_Pims_Department, UID_Pims_ParentDepartment, UID_PDir_Department, UID_PDir_ParentDepartment FROM dirs WHERE PDirTreeLevel > 0 ORDER BY PDirFullPath;

with rpt as ( select pop.DepartmentName as 'PopDepartmentName', org.FullPath as PopFullPath, org.DepartmentName as 'OrgDepartmentName', d.lev as 'lev', d.FullPath as 'Also Applies to Org' from Department pop inner join CCC_Population_Org po on po.CCC_UID_Population = pop.UID_Department inner join Department org on po.CCC_UID_Organisation = org.UID_Department cross apply [dbo].[Department_and_Subdepartments](org.UID_Department) d left outer join PersonInDepartment pd on d.UID_Department = pd.UID_Department ) selectx PopDepartmentName as "Populatie", PopFullPath as "FullPath", OrgDepartmentName as "Organisatie", lev as "Level", OrgFullPath as "Also Applies to Org" from rpt order by 1, 2, 5;

with rpt as ( select pop.DepartmentName as 'PopDepartmentName', org.FullPath as PopFullPath, org.DepartmentName as 'OrgDepartmentName', d.lev as 'lev', d.FullPath as 'OrgFullPath' from Department pop inner join CCC_Population_Org po on po.CCC_UID_Population = pop.UID_Department inner join Department org on po.CCC_UID_Organisation = org.UID_Department cross apply [dbo].[Department_and_Subdepartments](org.UID_Department) d left outer join PersonInDepartment pd on d.UID_Department = pd.UID_Department ) selectx PopDepartmentName as "Populatie", PopFullPath as "FullPath", OrgDepartmentName as "Organisatie", lev as "Level", OrgFullPath as "Also Applies to Org" from rpt order by 1, 2, 5;

with rpt as ( select pop.DepartmentName as 'Populatie', org.FullPath as 'OrgFullPath', d.FullPath as 'AlsoFullPath', p.LastName + ', ' + p.FirstName as 'Person' from Department pop inner join CCC_Population_Org po on po.CCC_UID_Population = pop.UID_Department inner join Department org on po.CCC_UID_Organisation = org.UID_Department cross apply [dbo].[Department_and_Subdepartments](org.UID_Department) d left outer join PersonInDepartment pd on d.UID_Department = pd.UID_Department left outer join Person p on pd.UID_Person = p.UID_Person where d.lev >= 0 --and not (p.UID_Person is null) ) select Populatie, OrgFullPath as "Organisatie", AlsoFullPath as "Also Applies to Org", Person from rpt order by 1, 2, 3, 4;

with rpt as ( select pop.DepartmentName as 'Populatie', org.FullPath as 'OrgFullPath', d.FullPath as 'AlsoFullPath', p.LastName + ', ' + p.FirstName as 'Person' from Department pop inner join CCC_Population_Org po on po.CCC_UID_Population = pop.UID_Department inner join Department org on po.CCC_UID_Organisation = org.UID_Department cross apply [dbo].[Department_and_Subdepartments](org.UID_Department) d left outer join PersonInDepartment pd on d.UID_Department = pd.UID_Department left outer join Person p on pd.UID_Person = p.UID_Person where d.lev >= 0 --and not (p.UID_Person is null) ) select Populatie, OrgFullPath as "Organisatie", AlsoFullPath as "Also Applies to Org", Person from rpt order by 1, 2, 3, 4;

WITH chain AS ( SELECT 'ADS_ADSAccount_Move_TerminalHome' as process_name ), adam AS ( SELECT FORMAT(ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY j.UID_Job), '0000#') AS row_num, j.Name, j.Description, j.UID_Job, j.UID_ErrorJob, j.UID_SuccessJob FROM chain, Job j INNER JOIN JobChain jc ON j.UID_JobChain = jc.UID_JobChain Where jc.Name = chain.process_name and not exists (select * from job j2 where j2.UID_SuccessJob = j.UID_Job Or j2.UID_ErrorJob = j.UID_Job) ), child AS ( SELECT adam.row_num + '.' + FORMAT(ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY j3.UID_Job), '0000#') AS row_num, j3.Name, j3.Description, j3.UID_Job, j3.UID_ErrorJob, j3.UID_SuccessJob FROM adam, Job j3 where adam.UID_SuccessJob = j3.UID_Job OR adam.UID_ErrorJob = j3.UID_Job ), grandchild AS ( SELECT child.row_num + '.' + FORMAT(ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY j4.UID_Job), '0000#') AS row_num, j4.Name, j4.Description, j4.UID_Job, j4.UID_ErrorJob, j4.UID_SuccessJob FROM child, Job j4 where child.UID_SuccessJob = j4.UID_Job OR child.UID_ErrorJob = j4.UID_Job ), tree AS ( SELECT row_num, Name, Description, UID_Job, UID_ErrorJob, UID_SuccessJob FROM adam UNION SELECT row_num, Name, Description, UID_Job, UID_ErrorJob, UID_SuccessJob FROM child UNION SELECT row_num, Name, Description, UID_Job, UID_ErrorJob, UID_SuccessJob FROM grandchild ), rpt AS ( SELECT t0.row_num As proc_id, t0.Name as proc_name, case when not err.UID_JOB is null then err.row_num else '' end AS next_id, case when not succ.UID_Job is null AND not err.UID_JOB is null then 'OK,ERROR' when not succ.UID_Job is null AND err.UID_JOB is null then 'OK' when succ.UID_Job is null AND not err.UID_JOB is null then 'ERROR' else '' end AS line_lable, case when t0.row_num = '00001' then 'Begin' when not succ.UID_Job is null AND not err.UID_JOB is null then 'Beslissing' else 'Proces' end AS type_shape, t0.Description As descr FROM tree t0 LEFT OUTER JOIN tree succ ON t0.UID_SuccessJob = succ.UID_Job LEFT OUTER JOIN tree err ON t0.UID_ErrorJob = err.UID_Job ) SELECT proc_id as "Processtap-id", proc_name as "Beschrijving van processtap", next_id AS "Id van volgende stap", line_lable As "Label van verbindingslijn", type_shape As "Shapetype", WITH Chains AS ( select distinct JobChainName from JobQueue ), Roots As ( select j.JobChainName, j.StartAt, j.UID_Job from Chains c inner join JobQueue j on c.JobChainName=j.JobChainName where j.IsRootJob = 1 ), Children As ( select 0 as lev, 0 as typ, r.JobChainName, r.StartAt As ProcessStartAt, j2.UID_Job, j2.UID_JobError, j2.UID_JobSuccess from Roots r inner join JobQueue j2 on r.UID_Job = j2.UID_Job union all select c.lev + 1 as lev, 1 as typ, c.JobChainName, c.ProcessStartAt, j3.UID_Job, j3.UID_JobError, j3.UID_JobSuccess from Children c inner join JobQueue j3 on c.UID_JobSuccess = j3.UID_Job union all select c.lev + 1 as lev, 2 as typ, c.JobChainName, c.ProcessStartAt, j4.UID_Job, j4.UID_JobError, j4.UID_JobSuccess from Children c inner join JobQueue j4 on c.UID_JobError = j4.UID_Job ), ParmUIDs AS ( SELECT DISTINCT UID_Tree FROM JobTreeParamColl ), ParmParms AS ( SELECT UID_Tree, CONCAT_WS('~', '', LEN(jp.ParameterName), jp.ParameterName, LEN(jp.ParameterValue), jp.ParameterValue, 0, '') As Parms FROM JobTreeParamColl jp ), ParmList As ( SELECT UID_Tree, (SELECT SUB.Parms AS [text()] FROM ParmParms SUB WHERE SUB.UID_Tree = CAT.UID_Tree FOR XML PATH('')) AS Parms FROM ParmUIDs CAT ), JobList as ( select c.JobChainName, c.ProcessStartAt, c.lev, 1000 * c.lev + c.typ as SortOrder, j.TaskName, j.Ready2EXE, j.Queue, j.StartAt, j.ErrorMessages, j.GenProcID, j.ParamIN, CONCAT(pl.Parms, '~') as BlueParms, j.UID_Job, j.UID_Tree from Children c inner join JobQueue j on c.UID_Job = j.UID_Job left outer join ParmList pl on j.UID_Tree = pl.UID_Tree ), RPT AS ( SELECT j.JobChainName, j.ProcessStartAt, j.lev, j.TaskName, j.Ready2EXE, j.Queue, j.StartAt, j.ErrorMessages, j.GenProcID, j.ParamIN, REPLACE(j.BlueParms,'',CHAR(13)) as BlueParms, j.SortOrder FROM JobList j INNER JOIN JobQueue jj on j.UID_Job = jj.UID_Job ) SELECT JobChainName as "Job", ProcessStartAt as "Job Start Time", lev as "<LEVEL>", TaskName as "Task", Ready2EXE as "Execution Status", Queue as "Executing server", StartAt as "Start time", ErrorMessages as "Errors", GenProcID, ParamIN as "Parameters", BlueParms from RPT order by JobChainName, PROCESSSTARTAT, SORTORDER;
